com.flowpowered.network.session

Class PulsingSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.network.session.BasicSession
      • com.flowpowered.network.session.PulsingSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Session

    public class PulsingSession
extends BasicSession
    Represents a BasicSession which has both a PulsingSession.State and PulsingSession.SendType. It can queue messages if needed.
